title: Winter PAC Meeting date
text: Winter PAC Meeting date Winter sports online registration is up and running now and CHS encourages parents and athletes to register early. Comment Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 10:51 AM Updated at 2:15 PM Posted Oct. 21, 2015 at 10:51 AM Updated at 2:15 PM The Winter Sports PAC meeting will be Monday November 2nd at 6:00pm at the CHS auditorium. Athletes and parents will meet with Mr. Garmen and then with the coach of their sport. Directions for registering online for activities will available. Also, the winter sports online registration is up and running now and CHS encourages parents and athletes to register early. By Times Staff
